# Checkpoints - KX Delta Platform

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/platform/checkpoints/

# Checkpoints

You can create checkpoints for the Control process with the Checkpoints
viewer.

## Create a checkpoint

  1. Pick _DC Checkpoint_ from the _Tools > Open Viewer_ menu.

![Screenshot](../img/control/checkpoints1.png)

  2. In the new viewer click _Set DC Checkpoint_.

![Screenshot](../img/control/checkpoints2.png)

  3. Enter a comment for the checkpoint and click _OK_.

![Screenshot](../img/control/checkpoints3.png)

You should see a new checkpoint.

![Screenshot](../img/control/checkpoints4.png)

## Revert to a checkpoint

  1. Choose a checkpoint from the list and use either the button or the menu item to revert.

![Screenshot](../img/control/checkpoints5.png)

  2. Click _OK_ to revert.

![Screenshot](../img/control/checkpoints6.png)

You should see a reversion to the checkpoint in the list.

![Screenshot](../img/control/checkpoints7.png)

